data.description: ASSUMBLE FHA RATE 3.75 AVAILABLE. Large oversized corner lot. Single story home newly built by MI Homes in 2020. Full of upgrades. Features 4 bedrooms / 2 baths / 2 car garage. Open floor plan kitchen, dinning , living room. High ceilings. Beautiful foyer as you first enter. Kitchen features large kitchen island, granite countertops, 42 inch white custom cabinets, walk in pantry, lots of cabinet space, OPEN FLOORPLAN! Large living and dinning room. Wood flooring, carpet in bedrooms, ceramic tile in bathrooms. Windows for natural lighting throughout. Stainless steel microwave, gas range, dishwasher. Master bedroom features a bay window with master bath large walk in shower, double vanity and walk in closet. Secondary bedrooms and secondary bathroom with one vanity and tub/shower combo. Flex room can be used as an office or 4 bedroom/guest room. Covered patio backyard. Very private. Large shed to convey. Energy Efficient with Radiant deck barrier and double pane windows. Builder 10 year limited warranty is transferable. Community amenities include park, playground, bike lanes, basketball court. MOTIVATED SELLER. OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY OCTOBER 14TH 1 TO 4 PM. Come see us!
